summary: Completed comprehensive testing of car dealership website. All major functionality working correctly including landing page, inventory with filters, car details, admin panel, and form submissions.
passed_tests: Backend API - All 22 endpoints working (cars, inquiries, contact, admin)
Landing page loads with hero section and featured cars
Navigation links work correctly (Inventory, About, Contact, Admin)
Featured cars section displays 6 cars from database
Inventory page with working filters (brand, price, year, fuel type)
Car detail page with image gallery and specifications
Inquiry form on car detail page submits successfully
Contact form on landing page submits successfully
Admin dashboard shows statistics (total vehicles, available, sold, inquiries)
Admin cars management - add, edit, delete functionality
Admin inquiries page shows customer inquiries with status updates
